269
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:42,440
 Malo,

270
00:15:42,440 --> 00:15:43,020
 ali eto.

271
00:15:43,020 --> 00:15:45,460
 Malo.

272
00:15:45,460 --> 00:15:47,700
 Kad bih mogao

