00:15:50,880 --> 00:15:52,780
 Jer volim čovjeka.

277
00:15:52,780 --> 00:15:54,340
 To je moje

278
00:15:54,340 --> 00:15:55,520
 opredjeljenje,

279
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:56,680
