 A što bi danas rekao?

303
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:44,780
 Život nije ljubljen.

304
00:16:44,780 --> 00:16:46,840
 Ne ljubav,

305
00:16:46,840 --> 00:16:48,400
 nego život nije ljubljen.

306
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:54,260
 Sve se nadzire,

307
00:16:54,260 --> 00:16:55,620
 sva budućnost,

308
00:16:55,620 --> 00:16:57,880
 znanost,

309
00:16:57,880 --> 00:16:58,500
 tehnika,

310
00:16:58,500 --> 00:16:59,520
 tehnologija,

311
00:17:01,340 --> 00:17:02,900
 mašta o lunjanju

312
00:17:02,900 --> 00:17:03,660
 po svemiru,

313
00:17:03,660 --> 00:17:05,220
 izmišljaju filmove

314
00:17:05,220 --> 00:17:07,320
