328
00:17:34,600 --> 00:17:36,800
 i sa zemlje

329
00:17:36,800 --> 00:17:38,820
 i iz podzemlja

330
00:17:38,820 --> 00:17:40,520
 i iz dubine mora

331
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:41,220
