341
00:18:10,240 --> 00:18:13,500
 Možete misliti Adama.

342
00:18:13,500 --> 00:18:16,840
 Sam na svijetu.

343
00:18:16,840 --> 00:18:18,140
 Ajde, zamislite sebe

344
00:18:18,140 --> 00:18:19,540
 da ste sami na svijetu,

345
00:18:19,540 --> 00:18:21,180
