354
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:39,680
 Ja sam.

355
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:44,200
 I ugleda nekog sebi sličnoga.

356
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:48,540
 I odmah zaboravi onoga

357
00:18:48,540 --> 00:18:50,680
