364
00:19:01,100 --> 00:19:02,280
 s Bogom u sebi.

365
00:19:02,280 --> 00:19:05,000
 I onda ti Bog nešto kaže,

366
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:06,320
 onda ti njemu nešto kažeš,

367
00:19:06,320 --> 00:19:07,660
