399
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:22,280
 Podlegao je toj napasti,

400
00:20:22,280 --> 00:20:23,200
 meni moje.

401
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:25,960
 To je moje.

402
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:31,260
 Najstražiji što sam,

403
00:20:31,260 --> 00:20:33,400
 najstrašniji prizor

404
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:34,180
 što sam ga vidio.

405
00:20:34,180 --> 00:20:36,800
 Jedna žena,

406
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:38,100
 dimi,

407
00:20:38,100 --> 00:20:40,660
 ko gradska toplana.

408
00:20:41,760 --> 00:20:42,540
 idu oblaci,

409
00:20:42,540 --> 00:20:43,200
 dima iz nje,

410
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:45,680
 valja se,

411
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:48,720
 onaj moj,

412
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:51,300
 onaj moj.

413
00:20:51,300 --> 00:20:54,200
 Nema ni imena,

414
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:55,140
 nego moj.

415
00:20:55,140 --> 00:20:59,860
 Moj će ti čovjek to napraviti,

416
00:20:59,860 --> 00:21:01,100
