417
00:21:03,600 --> 00:21:04,600
 ima ga.

418
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:07,660
 Zato izgleda ko avet.

419
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:11,060
 Našao, djavao,

420
00:21:11,060 --> 00:21:12,220
