430
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:45,180
 Kad je sve završio,

431
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:47,640
 kao šlag

432
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:48,840
 na tortu

433
00:21:48,840 --> 00:21:50,280
 Bog stavlja ženu.

434
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:55,220
 S najuzvišenijim poslanjem

435
00:21:55,220 --> 00:21:56,480
