437
00:21:57,800 --> 00:21:59,620
 svetog čovječanstva.

438
00:21:59,620 --> 00:22:03,640
 Uzmite litanije

439
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,740
 svetog Josipa.

440
00:22:04,740 --> 00:22:09,160
 I litanije gospine,

441
00:22:09,160 --> 00:22:10,340
