456
00:22:40,220 --> 00:22:42,020
 nego mora biti

457
00:22:42,020 --> 00:22:42,800
 nešto više.

458
00:22:45,020 --> 00:22:49,380
 E, sad sam se udala,

459
00:22:49,380 --> 00:22:50,300
