464
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:57,100
 Ma kako ćeš biti

465
00:22:57,100 --> 00:22:57,800
 ravnopravna?

466
00:22:57,800 --> 00:22:58,980
 Pa ne može

467
00:22:58,980 --> 00:22:59,600
