471
00:23:01,420 --> 00:23:02,300
 Kako će biti s tobom

472
00:23:02,300 --> 00:23:03,200
 ravnopravna?

473
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:06,700
 Ne, ja ću zapovjedati

474
00:23:06,700 --> 00:23:07,420
