483
00:23:16,220 --> 00:23:17,760
 koja ima

484
00:23:17,760 --> 00:23:18,740
 jedan jedini posao

485
00:23:18,740 --> 00:23:19,520
 da ubija ljude.

486
00:23:22,940 --> 00:23:24,120
 Makne one tamo,

487
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:26,220
 sad ovdje,

488
00:23:26,220 --> 00:23:27,040
 sad tamo,

489
00:23:27,040 --> 00:23:28,180
