494
00:23:33,540 --> 00:23:35,440
 Ima i koje to žele.

495
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:37,720
 Ako ne može tamo,

496
00:23:37,720 --> 00:23:39,320
 a bit će vojskovođa

497
00:23:39,320 --> 00:23:40,040
 u svojoj kući.

498
00:23:40,040 --> 00:23:44,280
 Zgazit će muža prvoga,

499
00:23:44,280 --> 00:23:46,980
 a onda djeci

500
00:23:46,980 --> 00:23:48,120
 pozavrtati vratove.

501
00:23:48,120 --> 00:23:50,620
 I naći svoju

502
00:23:50,620 --> 00:23:52,140
 najbolju prijateljicu,

503
00:23:52,320 --> 00:23:53,260
 jadna ona,

504
00:23:53,260 --> 00:23:56,380
 kakvog ona kretena

505
00:23:56,380 --> 00:23:57,220
 za muža ima,

506
00:23:57,220 --> 00:23:58,840
 a djeca,

507
00:23:58,840 --> 00:24:01,640
 i jedna takva

508
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:02,680
 iz one trojke

509
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:04,360
 govori za svoju djecu,

510
00:24:04,360 --> 00:24:06,040
 one moje zvijeri.

511
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:08,100
 Zvijeri.

512
00:24:08,100 --> 00:24:10,260
 Majka da za djete kaže zvijeri.

513
00:24:10,260 --> 00:24:17,980
 To je svijet u kojem mi živimo.

514
00:24:17,980 --> 00:24:19,460
 To je tragedija

515
00:24:19,460 --> 00:24:21,200
 u koju se čovjek

516
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:23,040
 ljubljeno Božje biće,

517
00:24:23,040 --> 00:24:24,520
 koje je stvoreno

518
00:24:24,520 --> 00:24:25,740
 da u njemu bude

519
00:24:25,740 --> 00:24:27,240
 Božja ljubav,

520
00:24:27,240 --> 00:24:28,360
 to je zduh sveti,

521
00:24:28,360 --> 00:24:31,280
 i Božja istina,

522
00:24:31,280 --> 00:24:33,580
 to je krist.

523
00:24:33,580 --> 00:24:38,260
 Razlika između

524
00:24:38,260 --> 00:24:39,140
 Božje istine

525
00:24:39,140 --> 00:24:41,140
 i ljudske istine

526
00:24:41,140 --> 00:24:41,920
 u tome što

527
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,220
 Boga reče i bi.

528
00:24:43,220 --> 00:24:50,740
 Kad kažeš

529
00:24:50,740 --> 00:24:52,080
 ovo drvo je jabuka,

530
00:24:52,080 --> 00:24:55,240
 onda to drvo zaista

531
00:24:55,240 --> 00:24:56,120
 jest jabuka

532
00:24:56,120 --> 00:24:57,520
 i zauvijek je jabuka,

533
00:24:57,520 --> 00:24:58,600
 a ovo je more

534
00:24:58,600 --> 00:24:59,800
 i zauvijek je more.

535
00:25:02,120 --> 00:25:02,860
 i kad kažeš

536
00:25:02,860 --> 00:25:03,960
 more je slano,

537
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:06,080
 onda je more

538
00:25:06,080 --> 00:25:07,540
 zauvijek slano,

539
00:25:07,540 --> 00:25:10,340
 jer Božja istina

540
00:25:10,340 --> 00:25:12,000
 istvara i održava.

541
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:18,840
 Zato je čovjek stvoren.

542
00:25:18,840 --> 00:25:20,380
 Da u njemu stanuje

543
00:25:20,380 --> 00:25:21,500
 Božja istina,

544
00:25:21,500 --> 00:25:22,580
 to je krist.

545
00:25:22,580 --> 00:25:25,460
 Bog je duh.

546
00:25:25,460 --> 00:25:29,480
 Porod duha je riječ.

547
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:32,500
 I čovjek je duh.

548
00:25:32,500 --> 00:25:33,620
 On bez nadahnuća

549
00:25:33,620 --> 00:25:34,640
 ne može ništa učiniti.

550
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,540
 Dođeš na večer,

551
00:25:35,540 --> 00:25:36,860
 gladam pred frižider,

552
00:25:36,860 --> 00:25:38,920
 nešto bi još pojevao,

553
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:39,640
 a ne znam što.

554
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:42,060
 Otvoriš i gledaš.

555
00:25:42,060 --> 00:25:45,300
 A gladam samo,

556
00:25:45,300 --> 00:25:46,200
 ne znam što bi jeo.

557
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:47,560
 A onda ti žena kaže,

558
00:25:47,560 --> 00:25:48,800
 a čuj, pa probaj toga sira.

559
00:25:48,800 --> 00:25:50,420
 A vidiš, dobro si se sjetila.

560
00:25:50,420 --> 00:25:51,220
 Može.

561
00:25:51,220 --> 00:25:52,260
 A tu je stajao.

562
00:25:52,260 --> 00:25:54,820
 Nije on imao nadahnuće,

563
00:25:54,820 --> 00:25:56,160
 nego ona dobila nadahnuće.

564
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:59,420
 Nadahnuće.

565
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:00,500
 Bez nadahnuća

566
00:26:00,500 --> 00:26:01,460
 ni jesti ne možeš.

567
00:26:01,460 --> 00:26:04,920
 Hajde nek neko

568
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:05,960
 bez nadahnuća

569
00:26:05,960 --> 00:26:07,340
 napravi sebi kuću.

570
00:26:07,340 --> 00:26:08,000
 Ne može.

571
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:12,500
 Pa kad je hoćeš napraviti,

572
00:26:12,500 --> 00:26:13,520
 ma radio bi,

573
00:26:13,520 --> 00:26:14,920
 ali ne znam kako ću je napraviti.

574
00:26:14,920 --> 00:26:16,600
 Moram sad nacrtati,

575
00:26:16,600 --> 00:26:17,280
 što mi treba.

576
00:26:17,280 --> 00:26:19,460
 Pa izračunati imam lija novaca

577
00:26:19,460 --> 00:26:20,540
 toliko da to napravim.

578
00:26:20,540 --> 00:26:22,300
 Pa onda napravi neko

579
00:26:22,300 --> 00:26:24,080
 da bude veća od susjeda.

580
00:26:24,080 --> 00:26:25,180
 Znam jednoga u ratu

581
00:26:25,180 --> 00:26:26,560
 koji je tri puta rušio kuću

582
00:26:26,560 --> 00:26:27,980
 da mu je kuća veća od bratove.

583
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:31,200
 Jer je on bogata brat,

584
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:32,540
 glupan koji ne zna zaraditi.

585
00:26:32,540 --> 00:26:33,780
 Jer ja se snađem.

586
00:26:33,780 --> 00:26:36,940
 A on ne zna živjeti.

587
00:26:43,600 --> 00:26:46,700
 Znači kao što je riječ Božja

588
00:26:46,700 --> 00:26:48,940
 porod Boga koji je ljubav,

589
00:26:48,940 --> 00:26:52,620
 tako je i riječ ljudska

590
00:26:52,620 --> 00:26:54,940
 porod čovjeka.

591
00:26:54,940 --> 00:26:59,320
 Vi ne znate tko sam ja dok ne progovorim.

592
00:26:59,320 --> 00:27:02,340
 Tako mi ne znamo

593
00:27:02,340 --> 00:27:04,620
 ni tko je Bog dok ne progovori.

594
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:08,320
 Imate onaj primjer

595
00:27:08,320 --> 00:27:12,400
 gdje apostoli i zabranici gospodinovi

596
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:14,180
 tri godine žive s njime.

597
00:27:14,180 --> 00:27:17,800
 I apostol Filip kaže

598
00:27:17,800 --> 00:27:20,000
 gospodine pokaži nam oca

599
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:20,920
 i bit će nam dobro.

600
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:22,460
 Bit će nam dosta.

601
00:27:22,460 --> 00:27:25,720
 A Jesu kaže

602
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:28,740
 Filipe, pa zar još ne razumiješ?

603
00:27:28,740 --> 00:27:31,680
 Tko je vidio mene

604
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:34,960
 vidio je i oca.

605
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:38,740
 Jer ja sam u ocu i otac u meni.

606
00:27:38,740 --> 00:27:41,400
 Tko je vidio Isusa,

607
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:43,020
 vidio je ljubav.

608
00:27:43,020 --> 00:27:44,380
 U njemu je ljubav vidljiva.

609
00:27:44,380 --> 00:27:48,360
 A i mi smo stvoreni

610
00:27:48,360 --> 00:27:50,760
 da ne vidljiva ljubav

611
00:27:50,760 --> 00:27:52,200
 u nama bude vidljiva

612
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:54,340
 i da ne vidljiva Božja istina,

613
00:27:54,340 --> 00:27:54,720
 Krist,

614
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:57,180
 i u nama bude vidljiva.

615
00:27:58,680 --> 00:27:59,400
 Pa se kaže

616
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:01,820
 ovaj čovjek je od riječi.

617
00:28:01,820 --> 00:28:05,500
 Ovo je dobar čovjek.

618
00:28:05,500 --> 00:28:11,320
 Da bi smo mogli biti

619
00:28:11,320 --> 00:28:14,200
 suradnici Božji,

620
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:16,680
 a to znači prava ljudska bića

621
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:20,520
 u kojima prebiva Božji duh,

622
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:23,020
 duh sveti ili ti ljubav

623
00:28:23,020 --> 00:28:25,880
 i Božja istina,

624
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,220
 da nema druge istine

625
00:28:27,220 --> 00:28:28,520
 una Mikoja Đavolska,

626
00:28:28,520 --> 00:28:28,980
 je li?

627
00:28:28,980 --> 00:28:31,360
 Mi moramo

628
00:28:31,360 --> 00:28:33,200
 i stodobno živjeti

629
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:34,200
 u dva svijeta.

630
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:38,140
 Kao društvena bića

631
00:28:38,140 --> 00:28:38,920
 u vanjskom,

632
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:42,660
 ali i kao osobe stvorene

633
00:28:42,660 --> 00:28:43,120
 da budu

634
00:28:43,120 --> 00:28:44,220
 hramovi duha

635
00:28:44,220 --> 00:28:45,180
 i istine Božje,

636
00:28:45,180 --> 00:28:47,160
 mi moramo živjeti

637
00:28:47,160 --> 00:28:47,980
 i s Bogom

638
00:28:47,980 --> 00:28:49,440
 u duhovnom svijetu.

639
00:28:51,820 --> 00:28:53,400
 i ako ne navraćamo

640
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:56,500
 u onaj govor,

641
00:28:56,500 --> 00:28:57,620
 onostrani,

642
00:28:57,620 --> 00:29:03,700
 na izvore istine Božje,

643
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:05,680
 mi ne možemo imati istine u sebi.

644
00:29:05,680 --> 00:29:10,400
 Mi žvaćemo ljudske govore.

645
00:29:12,580 --> 00:29:14,160
 Mi radimo što svi drugi dođu.

646
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:15,720
 Ajde, uđite u bilo koji stan,

647
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:17,600
 sve jedno je u koji ste ušli.

648
00:29:17,600 --> 00:29:20,520
 Isti namještaj,

649
00:29:20,520 --> 00:29:21,740
 isti raspored,

650
00:29:21,740 --> 00:29:24,000
 isto crno djavolsko oko

651
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,040
 u čošku mora biti

652
00:29:25,040 --> 00:29:25,980
 i kad ga ne gledaš.

653
00:29:29,120 --> 00:29:30,320
 Kad sam se počeo moliti

654
00:29:30,320 --> 00:29:32,760
 da Bog istira sve zle duhove

655
00:29:32,760 --> 00:29:34,120
 i nečiste sile iz moje kuće

656
00:29:34,120 --> 00:29:35,540
 nakon što odu u gosti,

657
00:29:35,540 --> 00:29:37,580
 da ti vidiš

658
00:29:37,580 --> 00:29:38,200
 da

659
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:41,700
 sa svakim čovjekom

660
00:29:41,700 --> 00:29:43,820
 ide sav njegov duhovni svijet.

661
00:29:43,820 --> 00:29:47,200
 A nema ni jednoga

662
00:29:47,200 --> 00:29:48,300
 koji nije sagriježio.

663
00:29:48,300 --> 00:29:49,640
 Dakle, kad god ti dođe

664
00:29:49,640 --> 00:29:50,720
 i najbolji prijatelj,

665
00:29:50,720 --> 00:29:52,100
 neki djava ostane u kući

666
00:29:52,100 --> 00:29:52,620
 kad on ode.

667
00:29:52,620 --> 00:29:55,120
 Iskoristio njega,

668
00:29:55,120 --> 00:29:56,160
 bio mu iza leđa

669
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:58,960
 i sad se raskomotio u tvojoj kući.

670
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:00,760
 I sve divno bilo,

671
00:30:00,760 --> 00:30:02,000
 samo se vi poslije svađate.

672
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:02,440
 Zašto?

673
00:30:02,440 --> 00:30:03,640
 Jer djavao neki je ostao tu.

674
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:06,660
 Ja kažem gospodine,

675
00:30:06,660 --> 00:30:07,520
 ja ljude primam,

676
00:30:07,520 --> 00:30:08,840
 ali njihove djavne ne primam.

677
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:12,120
 U ime Isusovo izlazite

678
00:30:12,120 --> 00:30:12,860
 svi zli du si

679
00:30:12,860 --> 00:30:14,240
 i nečiste sile iz ove kuće,

680
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:16,400
 jer ovu kuću posvećujem Bogu

681
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:17,280
 samo i nikom više.

682
00:30:17,280 --> 00:30:18,340
 I ljudskom rodu.

683
00:30:18,340 --> 00:30:19,520
 Može čovjek ući,

684
00:30:19,520 --> 00:30:21,080
 ali ne izdjavao njegov sanjenjime.

685
00:30:21,080 --> 00:30:24,100
 I kad tako počne moliti

686
00:30:24,100 --> 00:30:25,560
 da ti vidiš kad to počne pucati.

687
00:30:25,560 --> 00:30:27,200
 Ko vatromet

688
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:29,040
 puca iz poda

689
00:30:29,040 --> 00:30:30,040
 iz zidova,

690
00:30:30,040 --> 00:30:32,260
 a sa ekrana televizijskog

691
00:30:32,260 --> 00:30:33,860
 to samo što nisu strojnice.

692
00:30:33,860 --> 00:30:38,640
 Jer svi djavli svih filmova,

693
00:30:38,640 --> 00:30:39,460
 svih programa,

694
00:30:39,460 --> 00:30:41,720
 svih političkih laži i spletki,

695
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:43,840
 svih gadosti,

696
00:30:43,840 --> 00:30:46,560
 što ih svijet u paklu može naći,

697
00:30:46,560 --> 00:30:48,040
 sve tu stanuje.

698
00:30:48,040 --> 00:30:51,980
 Ajde, probaj se pomoliti

699
00:30:51,980 --> 00:30:53,160
 pred ugašanom televizijom.

700
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,300
 Ne možeš čovječe.

701
00:30:55,520 --> 00:30:56,280
 U najmanju ruku

702
00:30:56,280 --> 00:30:57,240
 zaspaš ćeš čim.

703
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:59,740
 Uzmeš pa ko krokodilu,

704
00:30:59,740 --> 00:31:00,620
 pucaju vilice,

705
00:31:00,620 --> 00:31:03,540
 oči zavrćeš

706
00:31:03,540 --> 00:31:04,180
 ko obsjednut,

707
00:31:04,180 --> 00:31:04,940
 ne zna šta ti je.

708
00:31:04,940 --> 00:31:07,700
 Ne možeš.

709
00:31:07,700 --> 00:31:08,920
 E onda trebaš

710
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:10,260
 dugo, dugo moliti

711
00:31:10,260 --> 00:31:11,320
 dok djavli ne odu.

712
00:31:11,320 --> 00:31:12,840
 Pa kad sjedneš tamo,

713
00:31:12,840 --> 00:31:13,440
 samo vidiš,

714
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:15,120
 šta će mi ovo smeće ovdje?

715
00:31:17,060 --> 00:31:17,920
 Bože, drage,

716
00:31:17,920 --> 00:31:18,820
 kakvo ruglo,

717
00:31:18,820 --> 00:31:19,960
 crno staklo,

718
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:20,640
 jedno oko.

719
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:22,100
 Bar da su dva,

720
00:31:22,100 --> 00:31:23,240
 ajde, pa bio bi sličan,

721
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:24,440
 imao bi ko naočale nešto.

722
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:29,660
 Moraš živjeti

723
00:31:29,660 --> 00:31:30,760
 da bi bio čovjek

724
00:31:30,760 --> 00:31:32,120
 u dva svijeta

725
00:31:32,120 --> 00:31:32,860
 istodobno.

726
00:31:32,860 --> 00:31:35,000
 Uvijek unutrini,

727
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:36,040
 odakle ti dolazi

728
00:31:36,040 --> 00:31:37,700
 unutrašnja Božja riječ.

729
00:31:37,700 --> 00:31:41,420
 I uvijek u mrako

730
00:31:41,420 --> 00:31:42,900
 ili ti zatvorenih očiju

731
00:31:42,900 --> 00:31:44,080
 odakle ti dolazi

732
00:31:44,080 --> 00:31:45,280
 Božje svijetlo.

733
00:31:46,600 --> 00:31:47,680
 Neko nadahnuće,

734
00:31:47,680 --> 00:31:48,540
 nekakva vizija

735
00:31:48,540 --> 00:31:49,540
 koju ti je Bog dao

736
00:31:49,540 --> 00:31:50,640
 kao mali signal,

737
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:52,640
 kao simboličku sliku

738
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:54,220
 nečega što ti želi reći

739
00:31:54,220 --> 00:31:56,220
 ili na što te nadahnjuje.

740
00:31:56,220 --> 00:32:01,200
 Jer čovjek je biće

741
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:03,080
 riječi i slike.

742
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:06,480
 I zanimljivo,

743
00:32:06,480 --> 00:32:08,560
 kao što je i sam,

744
00:32:08,560 --> 00:32:10,740
 nevidljiva duša

745
00:32:10,740 --> 00:32:12,120
 ima nevidljivu riječ.

746
00:32:12,120 --> 00:32:14,860
 A vidljivo tijelo

747
00:32:14,860 --> 00:32:16,280
 ima svoje ogledalo,

748
00:32:16,280 --> 00:32:17,420
 ima vidljivo nešto.

749
00:32:17,420 --> 00:32:20,400
 I jedno i drugo čovjek

750
00:32:20,400 --> 00:32:21,340
 treba biti.

751
00:32:21,340 --> 00:32:25,220
 I ako ti prebivaš

752
00:32:25,220 --> 00:32:27,280
 u mraku i tišini,

753
00:32:27,280 --> 00:32:28,160
 to sam danas govorio

754
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:29,100
 jednom bogoslovu,

755
00:32:29,100 --> 00:32:30,360
 rekao,

756
00:32:30,360 --> 00:32:31,400
 nemoj da te zavedu

757
00:32:31,400 --> 00:32:33,020
 puste teologije i priče,

758
00:32:33,020 --> 00:32:34,320
 jer će te ljudi

759
00:32:34,320 --> 00:32:35,200
 početi voditi

760
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:37,400
 u svoje nekakve konstrukcije.

761
00:32:37,940 --> 00:32:38,920
 nećeš naći Boga

762
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:39,580
 na taj način

763
00:32:39,580 --> 00:32:40,300
 da listaš.

764
00:32:40,300 --> 00:32:43,260
 Puste zapise.

765
00:32:43,260 --> 00:32:44,900
 Jao vama,

766
00:32:44,900 --> 00:32:45,800
 farizei,

767
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:46,780
 pismo znanci,

768
00:32:46,780 --> 00:32:48,880
 pismo znanci,

769
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:51,040
 danas se to ljepše zove,

770
00:32:51,040 --> 00:32:52,460
 to su teolozi,

771
00:32:52,460 --> 00:32:52,900
 znaš,

772
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:53,440
 možeš misliti,

773
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:54,020
 uzmeš Boga,

774
00:32:54,020 --> 00:32:54,840
 pa ga seciraš,

775
00:32:54,840 --> 00:32:55,760
 pa onda on izlazi

776
00:32:55,760 --> 00:32:56,140
 odavde,

777
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:56,740
 duh sveti,

778
00:32:56,740 --> 00:32:57,840
 pa ulazi tamo.

779
00:32:58,620 --> 00:32:59,580
 najveća tajna,

780
00:32:59,580 --> 00:33:00,420
 evo,

781
00:33:00,420 --> 00:33:01,460
 odmah su se svadili,

782
00:33:01,460 --> 00:33:03,200
 koliko je to stoljeća

783
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:05,260
 nakon apostolskog vjerovanja,

784
00:33:05,260 --> 00:33:06,160
 na jedan put su počeli

785
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:07,140
 krojiti odakle izlazi

786
00:33:07,140 --> 00:33:07,800
 duh sveti.

787
00:33:07,800 --> 00:33:10,300
 Dobro,

788
00:33:10,300 --> 00:33:11,040
 nije na meni to,

789
00:33:11,040 --> 00:33:12,080
 ali smo je malo čudili.

790
00:33:12,080 --> 00:33:14,100
 Najveća tajna

791
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:14,720
 naše vjere,

792
00:33:14,720 --> 00:33:16,580
 a vi se svadite

793
00:33:16,580 --> 00:33:17,440
 oko duha svetog,

794
00:33:17,440 --> 00:33:18,060
 a duh sveti je

795
00:33:18,060 --> 00:33:18,680
 duh jedinstva,

796
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:19,320
 ne razdora.

797
00:33:19,320 --> 00:33:21,780
 Pa nije još to dosta,

798
00:33:21,780 --> 00:33:22,640
 nego još izreknete

799
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:23,400
 proklinjanje.

800
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:24,980
 Kršten krštena proklinje,

801
00:33:24,980 --> 00:33:26,220
 jer se ne slaže

802
00:33:26,220 --> 00:33:26,880
 je duh sveti

803
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:27,940
 izišlo kroz ovu rupu

804
00:33:27,940 --> 00:33:28,580
 ili kroz onu.

805
00:33:28,580 --> 00:33:32,140
 Malo mi je čudno to,

806
00:33:32,140 --> 00:33:33,080
 nije na meni

807
00:33:33,080 --> 00:33:33,900
 da u to diram.

808
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:35,280
 I neću,

809
00:33:35,280 --> 00:33:36,260
 poštujem crkvu,

810
00:33:36,260 --> 00:33:37,460
 jer je to Božja tvorevina,

811
00:33:37,460 --> 00:33:38,940
 ali neke stvare

812
00:33:38,940 --> 00:33:39,740
 me zbunjuju,

813
00:33:39,740 --> 00:33:41,100
 volio bi da mi neko

814
00:33:41,100 --> 00:33:41,960
 objasni dublje,

815
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:43,200
 da me i ne bune toliko.

816
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:46,880
 Zato ja

817
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:48,060
 iz poštovanja

818
00:33:48,060 --> 00:33:50,200
 i priznanja crkve

819
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:51,200
 držim

820
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:52,920
 ovo teološko vjerovanje,

821
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:55,520
 ali onih neukih ljudi

822
00:33:55,520 --> 00:33:57,740
 apostola,

823
00:33:57,740 --> 00:33:59,040
 oni dvanest redaka,

824
00:33:59,040 --> 00:34:00,640
 to nekako,

825
00:34:00,640 --> 00:34:03,620
 kako da ti velim,

826
00:34:03,620 --> 00:34:04,580
 jasnije mi je

827
00:34:04,580 --> 00:34:05,480
 kad to pročitam.

828
00:34:05,480 --> 00:34:06,620
 To je neuka baka,

829
00:34:06,620 --> 00:34:07,400
 znaš šta je rekla.

830
00:34:08,760 --> 00:34:16,200
 zato idem na veću jednostavnost.

831
00:34:16,200 --> 00:34:19,580
 Ispravnije živiš

832
00:34:19,580 --> 00:34:21,440
 što manje znaš,

833
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,800
 a više dobra imaš.

834
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:26,380
 Ispravnije živiš

835
00:34:26,380 --> 00:34:28,280
 kad više žmiriš,

836
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:30,380
 odnosno spavaš

837
00:34:30,380 --> 00:34:33,860
 i kad više šutiš,

838
00:34:33,860 --> 00:34:35,400
 odnosno ne slušaš

839
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:36,420
 vajnske riječi.

840
00:34:36,420 --> 00:34:39,760
 Jer djavao

841
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:41,200
 i sav njegov svijet

842
00:34:41,200 --> 00:34:43,260
 izvana te ti dolazi

843
00:34:43,260 --> 00:34:44,600
 i odvlači te vani,

844
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:45,340
 zaboraviš.

845
00:34:45,340 --> 00:34:46,860
 Čovjek ne zna da srce ima

846
00:34:46,860 --> 00:34:48,700
 danas dok ga ne strefi infarkt.

847
00:34:48,700 --> 00:34:50,200
 Ajme,

848
00:34:50,200 --> 00:34:50,640
 zamisli,

849
00:34:50,640 --> 00:34:51,200
 imam srce.

850
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:55,040
 Jedan je u mom kraju govorio,

851
00:34:55,040 --> 00:34:55,400
 kaže,

852
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,940
 nemam srca.

853
00:34:56,940 --> 00:34:57,740
 Kako nemaš srca?

854
00:34:57,740 --> 00:34:59,260
 Porekao doktor da nemam srca.

855
00:34:59,260 --> 00:35:00,620
 On iskreno vjerovao,

856
00:35:00,620 --> 00:35:01,500
 jer je doktor rekao

857
00:35:01,500 --> 00:35:02,080
 da nema srca,

858
00:35:02,080 --> 00:35:02,900
 kucao u njemu.

859
00:35:02,900 --> 00:35:05,200
 Znači.

860
00:35:05,200 --> 00:35:08,400
 Tišina

861
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:11,200
 i mrak su

862
00:35:11,200 --> 00:35:12,880
 sredstva Božja

863
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:14,420
 gdje ćeš Boga sresti čuti.

864
00:35:14,420 --> 00:35:16,420
 I kad pogledaš

865
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:17,720
 ko su najveći

866
00:35:17,720 --> 00:35:19,880
 duhovni oci bili,

867
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:22,140
 najznačajniji Božji ljudi

868
00:35:22,140 --> 00:35:24,140
 na koje je Bog se mogao osloniti

869
00:35:24,140 --> 00:35:25,280
 da po njima nešto učini,

870
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:27,820
 to su upravo nekakvi takvi ljudi bili.

871
00:35:27,820 --> 00:35:30,740
 Jedan Abraham.

872
00:35:30,740 --> 00:35:34,320
 Kud ovce tudi on?

873
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:36,620
 I ima ih sve više.

874
00:35:36,620 --> 00:35:41,060
 Željan čovjeka ide onaj njegov

875
00:35:41,060 --> 00:35:42,800
 od brata mu,

876
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:43,480
 sin s njime,

877
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:43,880
 Lod.

878
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:47,740
 Kad se namnožilo tih puno ovaca,

879
00:35:47,740 --> 00:35:48,140
 kaže,

880
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:50,380
 rođače da nam se ne svađaju

881
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:52,060
 pastiri,

882
00:35:52,060 --> 00:35:53,840
 bilo bi dobro da se mi raziđemo.

883
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:56,460
 Evo ti se okreni okolo,

884
00:35:56,460 --> 00:35:58,000
 pa pogledaj kud god ti kreneš,

885
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:58,920
 ja ću na drugu stranu.

886
00:35:58,920 --> 00:36:01,560
 Dakle, Abraham nije izabrao ništa na zemlji.

887
00:36:01,560 --> 00:36:06,080
 A htio se rastati

888
00:36:06,080 --> 00:36:07,840
 od Lota

889
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:09,440
 da se ljudi ne svađaju.

890
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:10,840
 Dakle, stalo mu je bilo

891
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:12,300
 do ljubavi Božje među ljudima.

892
00:36:14,300 --> 00:36:15,080
 i Lod

893
00:36:15,080 --> 00:36:17,180
 oženio se

894
00:36:17,180 --> 00:36:19,600
 na kućnom savjetu,

895
00:36:19,600 --> 00:36:21,160
 dogovori se sa ženom kudbi,

896
00:36:21,160 --> 00:36:21,680
 ona kaže,

897
00:36:21,680 --> 00:36:22,260
 pogled dolje,

898
00:36:22,260 --> 00:36:23,580
 kakva ravnica,

899
00:36:23,580 --> 00:36:24,620
 grad,

900
00:36:24,620 --> 00:36:28,300
 ko će hodati za ovcama po ovim brdima,

901
00:36:28,300 --> 00:36:28,980
 idemo dolje,

902
00:36:28,980 --> 00:36:31,080
 izabere Sodomu.

903
00:36:31,080 --> 00:36:34,160
 I ovaj koji nije izabrao ništa,

904
00:36:34,160 --> 00:36:35,420
 dolazi mu Bog,

905
00:36:35,420 --> 00:36:37,100
 dolje povika nekakva.

906
00:36:37,100 --> 00:36:40,360
 Do neba se čuje koliko dolje se griješi

907
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:41,020
 u tome gradu

908
00:36:41,020 --> 00:36:43,060
 i ne vidjeti što je govoreo na tri anđela.

909
00:36:43,060 --> 00:36:47,620
 I savjetuju se sa tim čovjekom

910
00:36:47,620 --> 00:36:50,020
 koji je čovjek tišine i dobrote.

911
00:36:50,020 --> 00:36:52,700
 A on se zauzima

912
00:36:52,700 --> 00:36:55,520
 za spas grada.

913
00:36:55,520 --> 00:36:57,680
 I što god je tražio

914
00:36:57,680 --> 00:36:59,180
 taj prijatelj tišine

915
00:36:59,180 --> 00:37:00,760
 i razgovora s Bogom u sebi,

916
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:03,960
 sve je Bog bio spreman učiniti.

917
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:07,740
 Pa kad je došlo do zadnjih deset,

918
00:37:07,740 --> 00:37:09,180
 nije se usudio više pitati

919
00:37:09,180 --> 00:37:10,560
 jer je toliko Boga je samo čekao

920
00:37:10,560 --> 00:37:11,920
 što hoćeš, sve ću ti dati

921
00:37:11,920 --> 00:37:13,040
 zato što si moj.

922
00:37:13,040 --> 00:37:17,080
 I na zagovor Lota,

923
00:37:17,080 --> 00:37:18,800
 odnosno Abrahama,

924
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:20,960
 spašen je Lot

925
00:37:20,960 --> 00:37:23,120
 pravedniku,

926
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:24,680
 ali i njegova obitelj

927
00:37:24,680 --> 00:37:25,740
 koja nije bila sveta.

928
00:37:25,740 --> 00:37:29,300
 I što je Lot izgubio?

929
00:37:29,300 --> 00:37:30,740
 Je bio pravednik,

930
00:37:30,740 --> 00:37:31,520
 bojao se Boga,

931
00:37:31,520 --> 00:37:35,180
 ali je ipak bio čovjek

932
00:37:35,180 --> 00:37:37,240
 što se veli od krvi i mesa

933
00:37:37,240 --> 00:37:39,240
 od ove zemlje,

934
00:37:39,240 --> 00:37:41,260
 ostao je bez svega imanja,

935
00:37:41,260 --> 00:37:44,000
 ostao je bez žene

936
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:46,100
 koja se pretvorila u kip od stoli,

937
00:37:46,100 --> 00:37:49,360
 odnosno ogorčena je bila na Boga,

938
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:51,020
 zašto je ubija ljubavnike

939
00:37:51,020 --> 00:37:53,200
 i njezine najbolje prijateljice tamo

940
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:53,980
 i ne znam koji.

941
00:37:53,980 --> 00:37:56,680
 Ode, cijelo mi društvo ode.

942
00:37:57,180 --> 00:37:58,760
 Tako smo lijepo uštimali život,

943
00:37:58,760 --> 00:38:00,200
 bili smo najbolje prijateljice,

944
00:38:00,200 --> 00:38:01,220
 najbolji prijatelji,

945
00:38:01,220 --> 00:38:02,260
 podajno, stalno,

946
00:38:02,260 --> 00:38:04,240
 ko zna što je sve bilo tu.

947
00:38:04,240 --> 00:38:08,940
 Zato se pretvorila u kip od soli

948
00:38:08,940 --> 00:38:11,920
 i njezino ime nije zapamćeno.

949
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:14,180
 Jer koga Biblija spomene,

950
00:38:14,180 --> 00:38:16,460
 ta je zapamćen za uvijek.

951
00:38:16,460 --> 00:38:20,100
 U isto su vrijeme živjeli

952
00:38:20,100 --> 00:38:23,300
 Abraham i Sara

953
00:38:23,300 --> 00:38:25,920
 i Lot i njegova žena.

954
00:38:25,920 --> 00:38:26,540
 Zamislite,

955
00:38:26,540 --> 00:38:29,100
 Lotova žena nema imena u Bibliji.

956
00:38:29,100 --> 00:38:32,340
 Jer je žena ovog svijeta.

957
00:38:32,340 --> 00:38:34,280
 I kogod je čovjek samo ovog svijeta,

958
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:36,140
 njega zaboravguta,

959
00:38:36,140 --> 00:38:38,280
 ako je Boži čovjek,

960
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:39,680
 pamte ga sva vremena.

961
00:38:39,680 --> 00:38:43,460
 Kaže Isus, blago vama,

962
00:38:43,460 --> 00:38:45,680
 jer su vam imena zapisana na nebesima.

963
00:38:46,460 --> 00:38:48,500
 Ne gore na oblacima,

964
00:38:48,500 --> 00:38:50,060
 jer nisu to ta nebesa,

965
00:38:50,060 --> 00:38:52,340
 kad kažemo na nebu.

966
00:38:52,340 --> 00:38:55,860
 Nego su to unutrašnja nebesa

967
00:38:55,860 --> 00:38:57,460
 koja nadvisuju moju dušu.

968
00:38:57,460 --> 00:39:00,900
 Ono što je sve veće od moje naravi,

969
00:39:00,900 --> 00:39:03,300
 od moga postojanja,

970
00:39:03,300 --> 00:39:04,420
 stvoritelj moji,

971
00:39:04,420 --> 00:39:07,380
 on je na vrhu tih nebesa u meni.

972
00:39:07,380 --> 00:39:09,160
 I do tih nebesa dolaziš

973
00:39:09,160 --> 00:39:11,600
 s krušenom molitvom,

974
00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:14,580
 isključivanjem iz cijeloga svemira.

975
00:39:14,580 --> 00:39:16,480
 Sad sam samo pred tobom, Bože,

976
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:17,780
 koji si čista ljubav

977
00:39:17,780 --> 00:39:20,620
 i iščekujem tvoju riječ

978
00:39:20,620 --> 00:39:22,360
 da progovoriš mojoj duši.

979
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:24,920
 I bdiješ i čekaš

980
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:26,420
 i kad ta riječ dođe,

981
00:39:26,420 --> 00:39:28,460
 ti se preobraziš.

982
00:39:28,460 --> 00:39:29,680
 Jesi na zemlji,

983
00:39:29,680 --> 00:39:32,320
 ali si iznad zemlje,

984
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:34,360
 kao da je sav svemir u tebi,

985
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:37,280
 kao da si središnja točka svemira,

986
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:38,480
 tako se osjećaš.

987
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:40,940
 Govorim iz iskustva,

988
00:39:40,940 --> 00:39:42,180
 oni su bajke.

989
00:39:42,180 --> 00:39:45,520
 Gledaš sve od ozgo,

990
00:39:45,520 --> 00:39:46,160
 svi sina.

991
00:39:46,160 --> 00:39:48,220
 U snovima ti pokazuju od ozgo.

992
00:39:48,220 --> 00:39:53,540
 Uvijek ti od ozgo nekako pokazuje zemlju.

993
00:39:53,540 --> 00:39:58,260
 Ali si i konkretno sa svime tu.

994
00:39:58,260 --> 00:39:59,640
 Kad god ovdje dođeš,

995
00:39:59,640 --> 00:40:00,540
 koga god vidiš,

996
00:40:00,540 --> 00:40:03,300
 prilaziš mu ko najdražem svome.

997
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:07,320
 Jer je isti stvoritelj poželio imena i tebe.

998
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:12,380
 I kogod od nas krene krivim putem,

999
00:40:12,380 --> 00:40:14,900
 riječ Božja, Božja istina,

1000
00:40:14,900 --> 00:40:17,720
 Krist plače nad nama kao nad Jeruzalemom.

1001
00:40:17,720 --> 00:40:19,580
 O kad bi ti znao što te čeka,

1002
00:40:19,580 --> 00:40:22,100
 jer dolazi vrijeme kad će te neprijatelji tvoji

1003
00:40:22,100 --> 00:40:24,380
 okružiti sa svih strana

1004
00:40:24,380 --> 00:40:27,760
 i smrskati i tebe i djecu tvoju u tebi.

1005
00:40:27,760 --> 00:40:31,440
 Zato jer nisi priznao čas kad te Bog pohodi,

1006
00:40:31,560 --> 00:40:34,880
 odnosno kad ti savjest govori nije to dobro.

1007
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:37,960
 To je Božji glas u nama.

1008
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:40,500
 Savjest je Božja riječ.

1009
00:40:40,500 --> 00:40:43,240
 I ona nije dio ljudskog tijela,

1010
00:40:43,240 --> 00:40:44,360
 ni ljudske duše.

1011
00:40:44,360 --> 00:40:46,380
 Zato nju ne možeš ubiti.

1012
00:40:46,380 --> 00:40:49,320
 Ali pogledajte danas kolika je borba

1013
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,940
 protiv priziva savjesti.

1014
00:40:50,940 --> 00:40:52,780
 Zamisli, ja sam joj ubio u sebi

1015
00:40:52,780 --> 00:40:54,480
 i ti ćeš sad imati savjest kraj mene.

1016
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:57,060
 To treba zabraniti.

1017
00:40:57,060 --> 00:40:59,560
 Jer ako imaš savjest,

1018
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,560
 ne možeš krasti, ne možeš bludničiti,

1019
00:41:01,560 --> 00:41:02,740
 ne možeš ubijati,

1020
00:41:02,740 --> 00:41:04,520
 ne možeš mrziti,

1021
00:41:04,520 --> 00:41:07,300
 ne možeš u karijeri napredovati

1022
00:41:07,300 --> 00:41:09,160
 na lopovski način.

1023
00:41:09,160 --> 00:41:14,160
 To je ozbiljan problem u ovome društvu.

1024
00:41:14,160 --> 00:41:15,720
 Ne mislim Hrvatsko,

1025
00:41:15,720 --> 00:41:17,960
 nego uopće u ovoga vremena u svijetu.

1026
00:41:20,960 --> 00:41:24,480
 I zato je važno njegovati tišine

1027
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:28,300
 i poštivati mrak.

1028
00:41:28,300 --> 00:41:31,780
 Nije bitno koliko ćeš ti spavati.

1029
00:41:31,780 --> 00:41:35,960
 Ali je bitno kad uđeš na spavanje,

1030
00:41:35,960 --> 00:41:37,720
 nema ništa drugo, ne nosiš unutra.

1031
00:41:37,720 --> 00:41:39,540
 U tvoje ruke, oče,

1032
00:41:39,540 --> 00:41:40,520
 predajem duh svoj.

1033
00:41:40,520 --> 00:41:41,580
 Ja tako kažem.

1034
00:41:41,580 --> 00:41:43,900
 Jer je tako Isus rekao.

1035
00:41:43,900 --> 00:41:46,060
 A slijedom toga,

1036
00:41:46,060 --> 00:41:46,920
 u tvoje ruke,

1037
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:48,860
 Isuse, predajem dušu svoju.

1038
00:41:49,060 --> 00:41:51,820
 Jer je moja duša zarušnica riječi Božje.

1039
00:41:51,820 --> 00:41:53,560
 Duša govori

1040
00:41:53,560 --> 00:41:56,160
 i Bog duši govori,

1041
00:41:56,160 --> 00:41:57,560
 a to što Bog govori,

1042
00:41:57,560 --> 00:41:58,380
 to je riječ njegova,

1043
00:41:58,380 --> 00:41:58,960
 to je Hrist.

1044
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:01,440
 Koja tijelom postaje

1045
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:03,500
 kad ja predam svoje tijelo

1046
00:42:03,500 --> 00:42:05,540
 da riječ Božja u meni živi.

1047
00:42:05,540 --> 00:42:07,520
 Da ne govorim i ne mislim ništa drugo

1048
00:42:07,520 --> 00:42:08,820
 nego što Bog zapovjeda.

1049
00:42:08,820 --> 00:42:12,880
 I u tvoje ruke, duše sveti,

1050
00:42:12,880 --> 00:42:14,340
 predajem tijelo svoje

1051
00:42:14,340 --> 00:42:16,080
 jer je ono hram duha svetoga,

1052
00:42:16,080 --> 00:42:17,440
 kako kaže sveti Pavao.

1053
00:42:19,060 --> 00:42:20,300
 I kad ja sebe predam

1054
00:42:20,300 --> 00:42:21,480
 presvetome trojstvu

1055
00:42:21,480 --> 00:42:25,220
 i pet minuta je dosta

1056
00:42:25,220 --> 00:42:26,600
 da se ja dobro naspavam.

1057
00:42:26,600 --> 00:42:31,420
 Neće količina sname ne odmoriti,

1058
00:42:31,420 --> 00:42:34,300
 nego dodir

1059
00:42:34,300 --> 00:42:36,520
 presvetoga trojstva

1060
00:42:36,520 --> 00:42:38,440
 kad me dotakne

1061
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:40,880
 ja sam na novo.

1062
00:42:40,880 --> 00:42:44,860
 Ali probajte zažmiriti

1063
00:42:44,860 --> 00:42:47,440
 pa ćete vidjeti

1064
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:48,800
 kakve sve slike

1065
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:49,940
 iskaču pred vas.

1066
00:42:49,940 --> 00:42:51,480
 Prosudite jesu li Božje.

1067
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:53,760
 Vidjet ćete da svaki

1068
00:42:53,760 --> 00:42:55,980
 džavao nešto svoje gura unutra.

1069
00:42:55,980 --> 00:42:57,880
 Ili uplatnice,

1070
00:42:57,880 --> 00:42:59,560
 ili prizore nekakve tajne

1071
00:42:59,560 --> 00:43:00,860
 koje skrivaš od nekoga,

1072
00:43:00,860 --> 00:43:02,820
 ili nekakve uvrede tuđe.

1073
00:43:02,820 --> 00:43:05,080
 To ne možeš smiriti sliku u sebi.

1074
00:43:05,080 --> 00:43:09,400
 Isto tako,

1075
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:11,440
 zašutite

1076
00:43:11,440 --> 00:43:14,720
 i nemojte moliti dok ne budete

1077
00:43:14,720 --> 00:43:16,460
 u potpunoj tišini

1078
00:43:16,460 --> 00:43:18,060
 i najdublje miru

1079
00:43:18,060 --> 00:43:20,560
 gdje osjećate da je čitav svemir

1080
00:43:20,560 --> 00:43:21,580
 u tvom srcu.

1081
00:43:21,580 --> 00:43:25,620
 I da si ti u srednjega.

1082
00:43:25,620 --> 00:43:28,840
 Samo Bog je veći od tebe.

1083
00:43:28,840 --> 00:43:30,280
 Zamisi kolika je duša

1084
00:43:30,280 --> 00:43:31,500
 da čitav svemir

1085
00:43:31,500 --> 00:43:33,560
 i sva povijest ljudskog roda

1086
00:43:33,560 --> 00:43:35,440
 može stati u ljudsku dušu.

1087
00:43:36,180 --> 00:43:37,080
 U tijelo ne može,

1088
00:43:37,080 --> 00:43:38,680
 ali u dušu može.

1089
00:43:38,680 --> 00:43:41,640
 Jer duša može pojmiti

1090
00:43:41,640 --> 00:43:42,960
 sve što se događalo

1091
00:43:42,960 --> 00:43:44,640
 od stvaranja svijeta

1092
00:43:44,640 --> 00:43:46,940
 pa do završnice ove povijesti

1093
00:43:46,940 --> 00:43:48,200
 kad ćemo biti preneseni

1094
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:50,020
 u sasvim novi svijet.

1095
00:43:50,020 --> 00:43:51,680
 Isto nebo,

1096
00:43:51,680 --> 00:43:52,480
 ista zemlja,

1097
00:43:52,480 --> 00:43:53,520
 zapravo novo nebo

1098
00:43:53,520 --> 00:43:54,320
 i nova zemlja

1099
00:43:54,320 --> 00:43:55,260
 i nova tijela,

1100
00:43:55,260 --> 00:43:57,100
 ali ne više ova raspadljiva.

1101
00:43:57,100 --> 00:44:00,580
 Kad Isus kaže

1102
00:44:00,580 --> 00:44:02,140
 idem vam pripraviti stanove,

1103
00:44:02,140 --> 00:44:03,300
 u kući Oca moga ima

1104
00:44:03,300 --> 00:44:04,380
 mnogo stanova.

1105
00:44:05,580 --> 00:44:06,180
 Uvijek sam mislio

1106
00:44:06,180 --> 00:44:07,640
 kako će te vikendice gore

1107
00:44:07,640 --> 00:44:08,420
 biti na nebesima

1108
00:44:08,420 --> 00:44:09,360
 gdje ću ja biti sam

1109
00:44:09,360 --> 00:44:10,540
 pa ćemo mi tu lumariti.

1110
00:44:10,540 --> 00:44:13,200
 Nije tako.

1111
00:44:13,200 --> 00:44:14,240
 Isus govori

1112
00:44:14,240 --> 00:44:16,120
 on je zaručnik duša.

1113
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:18,580
 Riječ Božja govori

1114
00:44:18,580 --> 00:44:20,300
 o stanu duša,

1115
00:44:20,300 --> 00:44:21,960
 a stan duše je tijelo.

1116
00:44:21,960 --> 00:44:23,240
 Dakle, idem vam pripraviti

1117
00:44:23,240 --> 00:44:24,360
 uskrsna tijela.

1118
00:44:24,360 --> 00:44:28,500
 A ovo?

1119
00:44:28,500 --> 00:44:31,480
 Ovo je radno dijelo.

1120
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:34,220
 Ovo su čizme

1121
00:44:34,220 --> 00:44:35,640
 kojima hodaš kroz blato.

1122
00:44:35,640 --> 00:44:37,300
 To ih trebaš

1123
00:44:37,300 --> 00:44:38,180
 poderati

1124
00:44:38,180 --> 00:44:39,200
 da zaslužiš

1125
00:44:39,200 --> 00:44:40,800
 ući u svečano dijelo.

1126
00:44:40,800 --> 00:44:48,120
 I ovo ne vrijedi ništa.

1127
00:44:48,120 --> 00:44:49,560
 Kaže, tijelo ne vrijedi ništa.

1128
00:44:49,560 --> 00:44:52,220
 I to sam doživio.

1129
00:44:54,920 --> 00:44:55,340
 Kad sam

1130
00:44:55,340 --> 00:44:57,960
 negdje tamo,

1131
00:44:57,960 --> 00:44:58,900
 ne znam kada je to,

1132
00:44:58,900 --> 00:44:59,640
 koja godina bila,

1133
00:44:59,640 --> 00:45:00,680
 negdje 86-a,

1134
00:45:00,680 --> 00:45:01,420
 7-a, 8-a,

1135
00:45:01,420 --> 00:45:02,060
 kad sam ja počeo

1136
00:45:02,060 --> 00:45:03,080
 intenzivnije moliti,

1137
00:45:03,080 --> 00:45:07,980
 onda su u domu sindikata

1138
00:45:07,980 --> 00:45:08,620
 u Beogradu

1139
00:45:08,620 --> 00:45:09,140
 bili oni

1140
00:45:09,140 --> 00:45:10,100
 proslave

1141
00:45:10,100 --> 00:45:11,080
 dana Republike

1142
00:45:11,080 --> 00:45:12,520
 i svaka

1143
00:45:12,520 --> 00:45:14,160
 radio postaja

1144
00:45:14,160 --> 00:45:15,700
 svih Republika

1145
00:45:15,700 --> 00:45:16,380
 u Jugoslaviji

1146
00:45:16,380 --> 00:45:17,180
 je trebala postati

1147
00:45:17,180 --> 00:45:18,120
 po dva glumca

1148
00:45:18,120 --> 00:45:19,980
 u tu svečanost tamo.

1149
00:45:19,980 --> 00:45:21,720
 Radio Zagreba,

1150
00:45:21,720 --> 00:45:22,580
 odnosno Hrvatsku,

1151
00:45:22,680 --> 00:45:24,100
 trebali smo predstavljati

1152
00:45:24,100 --> 00:45:25,300
 ja i Vera Zima.

1153
00:45:25,300 --> 00:45:28,900
 A ja

1154
00:45:28,900 --> 00:45:31,800
 otkrio sve to pismo,

1155
00:45:31,800 --> 00:45:33,420
 oduševio se za tu riječ.

1156
00:45:33,420 --> 00:45:35,680
 Čitaj svaki dan,

1157
00:45:35,680 --> 00:45:36,740
 žmiri, moli,

1158
00:45:36,740 --> 00:45:37,940
 iščekuj riječ

1159
00:45:37,940 --> 00:45:39,540
 i sad možeš misliti,

1160
00:45:39,540 --> 00:45:40,580
 moram sad tri dana

1161
00:45:40,580 --> 00:45:41,400
 ići tamo-tamo,

1162
00:45:41,400 --> 00:45:42,460
 niti mogu otići u crku,

1163
00:45:42,460 --> 00:45:43,060
 niti znam.

1164
00:45:43,060 --> 00:45:44,440
 Ma da mi je naći

1165
00:45:44,440 --> 00:45:45,420
 bilo koga

1166
00:45:45,420 --> 00:45:48,020
 ko vjeruje tamo,

1167
00:45:48,020 --> 00:45:48,600
 samo da čujem

1168
00:45:48,600 --> 00:45:49,740
 kako ljudi tamo vjeruju.

1169
00:45:49,740 --> 00:45:52,120
 Uđem u autobus,

1170
00:45:52,180 --> 00:45:52,980
 idem na posao

1171
00:45:52,980 --> 00:45:55,180
 i opazim jednoga

1172
00:45:55,180 --> 00:45:55,980
 trombonistu

1173
00:45:55,980 --> 00:45:57,200
 iz kazališta Komedija.

1174
00:45:57,200 --> 00:45:59,160
 Poznavao sam ga

1175
00:45:59,160 --> 00:46:00,020
 ovako,

1176
00:46:00,020 --> 00:46:00,500
 izvanjski,

1177
00:46:00,500 --> 00:46:01,700
 ali nikad nismo razgovarali,

1178
00:46:01,700 --> 00:46:02,460
 stanuje kod mene

1179
00:46:02,460 --> 00:46:03,420
 tamo u Velikoj Gorici.

1180
00:46:05,640 --> 00:46:07,160
 i priđem ja njemu

1181
00:46:07,160 --> 00:46:08,800
 i sad mislim,

1182
00:46:08,800 --> 00:46:10,100
 kako bi ja njega pitao,

1183
00:46:10,100 --> 00:46:11,040
 jer znam da je on

1184
00:46:11,040 --> 00:46:12,980
 iz Beograda došao tamo.

1185
00:46:12,980 --> 00:46:15,120
 1971. godine,

1186
00:46:15,120 --> 00:46:17,480
 njegov najbolji prijatelj,

1187
00:46:17,480 --> 00:46:17,960
 Hrvat,

1188
00:46:17,960 --> 00:46:19,720
 je bio u orkestru,

1189
00:46:19,720 --> 00:46:22,040
 skupa s njim je svirao,

1190
00:46:22,040 --> 00:46:24,820
 i onda kad je zapalio se tamo

1191
00:46:24,820 --> 00:46:25,940
 srpski nacionalizam,

1192
00:46:27,120 --> 00:46:28,560
 vrijeđali se ovog prijatelja

1193
00:46:28,560 --> 00:46:30,000
 i ovaj iz solidarnosti

1194
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:31,440
 napusti orkestar

1195
00:46:31,440 --> 00:46:33,380
 radiotelevizije Beograd

1196
00:46:33,380 --> 00:46:35,720
 i dođe ovdje u Zagrebu

1197
00:46:35,720 --> 00:46:36,680
 kazalište Komediju.

1198
00:46:36,760 --> 00:46:37,840
 Međutim, ovdje ga dočeka

1199
00:46:37,840 --> 00:46:39,480
 slična vatra s hrvatske strane,

1200
00:46:39,480 --> 00:46:40,620
 jer on je crnogorac.

1201
00:46:40,620 --> 00:46:44,920
 I on nije se vratio u Beograd,

1202
00:46:44,920 --> 00:46:46,320
 nego je otišao u Kajro

1203
00:46:46,320 --> 00:46:47,940
 na nekakav turistički brod,

1204
00:46:47,940 --> 00:46:49,440
 pa kao izvrstan džezista,

1205
00:46:49,440 --> 00:46:51,180
 svirao dvije godine tamo

1206
00:46:51,180 --> 00:46:52,400
 dok se nije sredio malo

1207
00:46:52,400 --> 00:46:54,040
 i dođe i još uvijek je tu,

1208
00:46:54,040 --> 00:46:54,980
 ako nije umrao,

1209
00:46:54,980 --> 00:46:57,740
 u kazalištu Komedija bio.

1210
00:46:57,740 --> 00:46:58,980
 Ja vidim njega

1211
00:46:58,980 --> 00:47:00,180
 i znam da je o to da rekao,

1212
00:47:00,180 --> 00:47:01,600
 pa kad bi njega mogao pitati

1213
00:47:01,600 --> 00:47:02,880
 ima li nekog pobožnog,

1214
00:47:02,880 --> 00:47:04,160
 samo da sretnem čovjeka.

1215
00:47:06,760 --> 00:47:13,880
 Da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da, da.

1216
00:47:13,880 --> 00:47:17,160
 Meni se smrzle kosti.

1217
00:47:17,160 --> 00:47:18,980
 Rekao, je li ovaj lud, šta je ovo?

1218
00:47:18,980 --> 00:47:21,300
 Pa je li on uopće čovjek?

1219
00:47:21,300 --> 00:47:22,940
 Da to nije Andjeo Boži koji govori,

1220
00:47:22,940 --> 00:47:26,400
 pa budalo, jedna ti ideš u osinjak tamo progona crkve

1221
00:47:26,400 --> 00:47:27,740
 i ti bi išao sad po crkvama.

1222
00:47:27,740 --> 00:47:30,260
 Ja sam odlučio, neću ja ništa tamo,

1223
00:47:30,260 --> 00:47:32,100
 ovo ću odraditi i vratim se samo natrag.

1224
00:47:32,100 --> 00:47:34,460
 I onda počnemo mi priču o normalno.

1225
00:47:35,600 --> 00:47:37,000
 Kako si, što si, što radiš?

1226
00:47:37,000 --> 00:47:38,740
 Rekao, a u zadnje vrijeme otkrio Bibliju,

1227
00:47:38,740 --> 00:47:41,600
 pa sam, evo, baš me oduševljava.

1228
00:47:41,600 --> 00:47:43,660
 A je, to je zanimljiva knjiga

1229
00:47:43,660 --> 00:47:45,480
 i mi 20 minuta pričamo.

1230
00:47:45,480 --> 00:47:48,700
 Dođemo do glavnog kolodvora,

1231
00:47:48,700 --> 00:47:49,680
 stane autobus

1232
00:47:49,680 --> 00:47:52,760
 i mi koji iz kakve komedije,

1233
00:47:52,760 --> 00:47:55,340
 izvoljte, izvoljte vi, izvoljte vi, izvoljte vi.

1234
00:47:55,340 --> 00:47:56,500
 Nad dvojisa se pogađamo,

1235
00:47:56,500 --> 00:47:58,040
 ko će koga pustiti da iziđe.

1236
00:47:58,120 --> 00:47:59,160
 Međutim izišli svi.

1237
00:47:59,160 --> 00:48:01,160
 Ovaj već ubacio,

1238
00:48:01,160 --> 00:48:02,380
 brzinu kreće autobus,

1239
00:48:02,380 --> 00:48:03,660
 nema šta se više pogađati.

1240
00:48:03,660 --> 00:48:04,680
 Ja krenem dolje,

1241
00:48:04,680 --> 00:48:06,840
 a on mi tu iza ljevog uha kaže,

1242
00:48:06,840 --> 00:48:08,400
 ode Branko Ćopić,

1243
00:48:08,400 --> 00:48:09,500
 tarabe, tarabe.

1244
00:48:09,500 --> 00:48:11,060
 Ja šokiranu,

1245
00:48:11,060 --> 00:48:12,280
 odkud mi u selo uđe,

1246
00:48:12,280 --> 00:48:13,840
 jer Branko Ćopić u mom selu rođen.

1247
00:48:13,840 --> 00:48:16,080
 Ja dobio ime po njegovom bratu,

1248
00:48:16,080 --> 00:48:17,220
 koji je bio najbolji prijatelj

1249
00:48:17,220 --> 00:48:17,760
 moga oca.

1250
00:48:17,760 --> 00:48:19,220
 I mislim,

1251
00:48:19,220 --> 00:48:20,860
 kud mi ovaj sad uletio ovdje?

1252
00:48:20,860 --> 00:48:21,880
 Malo prije onakog,

1253
00:48:21,880 --> 00:48:22,340
 toliko,

1254
00:48:22,340 --> 00:48:24,500
 policijska sirena sad.

1255
00:48:24,500 --> 00:48:26,860
 Ja se okrenem,

1256
00:48:26,860 --> 00:48:27,680
 čovjek nestao,

1257
00:48:27,680 --> 00:48:28,140
 nema ga.

1258
00:48:28,140 --> 00:48:30,440
 Ne mogu vjerovati.

1259
00:48:30,440 --> 00:48:32,060
 Stojim na kolodvoru,

1260
00:48:32,060 --> 00:48:32,720
 okrećem se.

1261
00:48:32,720 --> 00:48:34,760
 Igrao sam predstavu tamo,

1262
00:48:34,760 --> 00:48:38,080
 onaj društveni dom Trešnjevka

1263
00:48:38,080 --> 00:48:39,140
 na onom parku,

1264
00:48:39,140 --> 00:48:40,000
 ne znam kako se zove,

1265
00:48:40,000 --> 00:48:41,320
 sad zove.

1266
00:48:41,320 --> 00:48:44,120
 Odigram predstavu,

1267
00:48:44,120 --> 00:48:45,220
 odem u komediju gore,

1268
00:48:45,220 --> 00:48:46,760
 pitan portira,

1269
00:48:46,840 --> 00:48:47,760
 je li bio Radmilo tu?

1270
00:48:47,760 --> 00:48:48,460
 Je, je, kaže,

1271
00:48:48,460 --> 00:48:49,160
 sad je otišao,

1272
00:48:49,160 --> 00:48:49,820
 imao je progup,

1273
00:48:49,820 --> 00:48:50,100
 pa otišao,

1274
00:48:50,100 --> 00:48:50,940
 hvala Bogu,

1275
00:48:50,940 --> 00:48:51,700
 nek je samo živ.

1276
00:48:51,700 --> 00:48:53,880
 Pa kakav je on čovjek?

1277
00:48:53,880 --> 00:48:54,520
 Ma kaže,

1278
00:48:54,520 --> 00:48:56,120
 ma on je jako pošten,

1279
00:48:56,120 --> 00:48:56,780
 dobar čovjek,

1280
00:48:56,780 --> 00:48:57,560
 ali je malo čudan.

1281
00:48:57,560 --> 00:48:57,840
 Rekao,

1282
00:48:57,840 --> 00:48:59,220
 meni je i previše čudan.

1283
00:48:59,220 --> 00:49:02,980
 I sad prođe neko vrijeme,

1284
00:49:02,980 --> 00:49:03,880
 ja njega sretnemu,

1285
00:49:03,880 --> 00:49:05,260
 ono vrijeme su počeli dućani

1286
00:49:05,260 --> 00:49:06,160
 raditi nedjeljom.

1287
00:49:06,160 --> 00:49:08,120
 Samo nas dvojica

1288
00:49:08,120 --> 00:49:08,960
 i prodavačica.

1289
00:49:08,960 --> 00:49:09,280
 E, re,

1290
00:49:09,280 --> 00:49:10,440
 re, sad mi nećeš povijeći.

1291
00:49:12,260 --> 00:49:14,080
 Mene zanima što se ono dogodilo.

1292
00:49:14,080 --> 00:49:15,400
 Ja ću ti reći što sam ja vidio,

1293
00:49:15,400 --> 00:49:16,860
 a ti meni reci što si ti vidio.

1294
00:49:16,860 --> 00:49:19,120
 Ja kažem,

1295
00:49:19,120 --> 00:49:20,000
 ja zakoracio dolje,

1296
00:49:20,000 --> 00:49:20,720
 a ti meni udari.

1297
00:49:20,720 --> 00:49:23,320
 Uleti mi u Branka Ćopića.

1298
00:49:23,320 --> 00:49:24,100
 Ode Branko Ćopić,

1299
00:49:24,100 --> 00:49:24,880
 tarabe, tarabe.

1300
00:49:25,120 --> 00:49:26,120
 Jer on bio potrešten,

1301
00:49:26,120 --> 00:49:27,000
 bio mu je susjed

1302
00:49:27,000 --> 00:49:29,340
 na Stubišu tamo kad je stanovao

1303
00:49:29,340 --> 00:49:30,280
 dobar čovjek,

1304
00:49:30,280 --> 00:49:31,460
 pa je odlučio

1305
00:49:31,460 --> 00:49:33,620
 ubiti se,

1306
00:49:33,620 --> 00:49:35,320
 jer on je bio društven čovjek,

1307
00:49:35,320 --> 00:49:36,280
 a u takvom društvu

1308
00:49:36,280 --> 00:49:38,020
 gdje su se svi ogradili,

1309
00:49:38,020 --> 00:49:39,320
 nema smisla živ...

1310
00:49:39,320 --> 00:49:41,700
 I on je tako okončao život.

1311
00:49:41,700 --> 00:49:42,340
 Jel'i?

1312
00:49:42,340 --> 00:49:44,980
 On je inače doživio

1313
00:49:44,980 --> 00:49:46,140
 jednu strašnu tragediju.

1314
00:49:46,140 --> 00:49:47,640
 Njemu je udba ubila ženu.

1315
00:49:47,640 --> 00:49:50,180
 Neku doktoricu.

1316
00:49:50,180 --> 00:49:51,420
 On došao doma,

1317
00:49:51,420 --> 00:49:52,380
 našao je u komadima

1318
00:49:52,380 --> 00:49:53,840
 sasjećenu bračnom krevetu.

1319
00:49:53,960 --> 00:49:54,920
 Tako da je on strašno

1320
00:49:54,920 --> 00:49:55,600
 nešto doživio.

1321
00:49:55,600 --> 00:49:57,360
 A onda su mu pljeskali

1322
00:49:57,360 --> 00:49:59,460
 veliki pjesnik

1323
00:49:59,460 --> 00:50:01,040
 i onda kad je vidio

1324
00:50:01,040 --> 00:50:01,940
 ušto se društvo

1325
00:50:01,940 --> 00:50:03,160
 pretvorilo,

1326
00:50:03,160 --> 00:50:05,020
 to je bila njegova potreštenost.

1327
00:50:05,020 --> 00:50:05,540
 Ja kažem,

1328
00:50:05,540 --> 00:50:07,160
 i ti meni kažeš tu rečenicu

1329
00:50:07,160 --> 00:50:07,900
 i ti nestao.

1330
00:50:07,900 --> 00:50:08,480
 Kaže, da.

1331
00:50:08,480 --> 00:50:09,260
 Ma kako da?

1332
00:50:09,260 --> 00:50:11,060
 Ja nisam doživio

1333
00:50:11,060 --> 00:50:11,920
 da sam ja nestao,

1334
00:50:11,920 --> 00:50:12,880
 nego oko mene

1335
00:50:12,880 --> 00:50:14,000
 je svega nestalo.

1336
00:50:14,000 --> 00:50:15,760
 Ja sam samo vidio

1337
00:50:15,760 --> 00:50:17,360
 pred sobom neki tamni križ,

1338
00:50:17,360 --> 00:50:19,160
 ne znam ti opisati

1339
00:50:19,160 --> 00:50:20,120
 kakva je to boja,

1340
00:50:20,120 --> 00:50:21,680
 ne znam ni koliko je trajilo,

1341
00:50:21,680 --> 00:50:22,980
 jer nemaš osjećaj vremena.

1342
00:50:23,960 --> 00:50:25,620
 I kad je to prestalo,

1343
00:50:25,620 --> 00:50:26,480
 ja sam se našao

1344
00:50:26,480 --> 00:50:27,820
 na istom mjestu,

1345
00:50:27,820 --> 00:50:28,800
 samo nema autobusa,

1346
00:50:28,800 --> 00:50:29,460
 nema vas.

1347
00:50:29,460 --> 00:50:30,580
 Ali meni se često

1348
00:50:30,580 --> 00:50:31,720
 svašta dogodi, kaže.

1349
00:50:31,720 --> 00:50:35,580
 Dakle, nestalo je tijelo,

1350
00:50:35,580 --> 00:50:37,420
 a čovjek nije nestao.

1351
00:50:37,420 --> 00:50:40,180
 I pojavio se čovjek opet.

1352
00:50:40,180 --> 00:50:43,560
 Čovjek nije tijelo.

1353
00:50:43,560 --> 00:50:46,340
 Čovjek je ono

1354
00:50:46,340 --> 00:50:47,760
 što u tijelu živi.

1355
00:50:49,920 --> 00:50:51,660
 Duša je neuništiva.

1356
00:50:51,660 --> 00:50:53,860
 Ona je vječna,

1357
00:50:53,860 --> 00:50:56,100
 ona ne može biti ni bolesna.

1358
00:50:56,100 --> 00:50:57,520
 Jer kad kažu

1359
00:50:57,520 --> 00:50:59,080
 psihička bolest,

1360
00:50:59,080 --> 00:51:00,040
 psiha je duša,

1361
00:51:00,040 --> 00:51:00,260
 jeli.

1362
00:51:00,260 --> 00:51:02,340
 Ma ne može duša biti bolesna

1363
00:51:02,340 --> 00:51:03,100
 ako je vječna.

1364
00:51:03,100 --> 00:51:04,340
 Ono što može biti bolesno,

1365
00:51:04,340 --> 00:51:05,240
 to može propasti.

1366
00:51:07,320 --> 00:51:08,340
 To nije vječno.

1367
00:51:08,340 --> 00:51:11,000
 Tako sam,

1368
00:51:11,000 --> 00:51:13,480
 kad me nazvala jedna djevojka

1369
00:51:13,480 --> 00:51:14,480
 iz Belog manastira,

1370
00:51:14,480 --> 00:51:16,820
 mama me spremila na psihijatriju,

1371
00:51:16,820 --> 00:51:17,580
 bi se pomolili,

1372
00:51:17,580 --> 00:51:19,200
 ja počeo moliti tu jednu očinsku

1373
00:51:19,200 --> 00:51:19,880
 svoju molitvu,

1374
00:51:19,880 --> 00:51:20,520
 koja baš

1375
00:51:20,520 --> 00:51:22,560
 puno milosti da.

1376
00:51:22,560 --> 00:51:26,320
 A iz nje jedan ružni,

1377
00:51:26,320 --> 00:51:28,620
 odvratni glas,

1378
00:51:28,620 --> 00:51:30,460
 proklet bio,

1379
00:51:30,460 --> 00:51:32,140
 nećeš mi je oteti.

1380
00:51:32,140 --> 00:51:33,840
 Ja maknem,

1381
00:51:33,840 --> 00:51:35,120
 slušali su i nastavim molitvu

1382
00:51:35,120 --> 00:51:36,400
 do kraja kad sam završavao

1383
00:51:36,400 --> 00:51:37,040
 zahvalu,

1384
00:51:37,040 --> 00:51:39,400
 lijepi djevojački glas

1385
00:51:39,400 --> 00:51:40,280
 kao na početku

1386
00:51:40,280 --> 00:51:42,160
 završava molitvu zahvala

1387
00:51:42,160 --> 00:51:42,760
 i ja mislim,

1388
00:51:42,760 --> 00:51:43,300
 čekaj,

1389
00:51:43,300 --> 00:51:46,960
 otkud bolesti inteligencija

1390
00:51:46,960 --> 00:51:48,540
 da složi takvu rečenicu?

1391
00:51:48,540 --> 00:51:49,640
 Proklet bio,

1392
00:51:49,640 --> 00:51:50,900
 nećeš mi je oteti.

1393
00:51:50,900 --> 00:51:54,700
 I zar je bolest glumac

1394
00:51:54,700 --> 00:51:56,800
 da može od djevojačkog glasa

1395
00:51:56,800 --> 00:51:58,980
 napraviti takvu transformaciju

1396
00:51:58,980 --> 00:52:00,640
 ko onaj najružniji,

1397
00:52:00,640 --> 00:52:02,060
 prostački, pljuvački,

1398
00:52:02,060 --> 00:52:03,080
 starački glas,

1399
00:52:03,080 --> 00:52:03,800
 što može biti,

1400
00:52:03,800 --> 00:52:05,000
 onaj poderani do kraja

1401
00:52:05,000 --> 00:52:05,780
 više nije ljudski

1402
00:52:05,780 --> 00:52:06,480
 nego zvjerski.

1403
00:52:06,480 --> 00:52:08,600
 I ostalom,

1404
00:52:08,600 --> 00:52:09,140
 što ona radi

1405
00:52:09,140 --> 00:52:10,080
 na psihijatri onda?

1406
00:52:10,080 --> 00:52:15,700
 Duhovni svijet.

1407
00:52:15,700 --> 00:52:18,960
 Do dana današnjeg se

1408
00:52:18,960 --> 00:52:21,160
 spominje

1409
00:52:21,160 --> 00:52:23,500
 epilepsija,

1410
00:52:23,500 --> 00:52:25,180
 bolest.

1411
00:52:26,320 --> 00:52:28,560
 čitajte u Evanđelju kako je onoga

1412
00:52:28,560 --> 00:52:31,040
 epileptičara Isus ozdravio,

1413
00:52:31,040 --> 00:52:33,360
 tako što je istirao zloga duha iz njega.

1414
00:52:33,360 --> 00:52:35,400
 Zapovjedio duhu,

1415
00:52:35,400 --> 00:52:37,380
 pa on omlat izgledao kao je ovakav.

1416
00:52:37,380 --> 00:52:40,020
 A ovdje se liječiš, liječiš,

1417
00:52:40,020 --> 00:52:41,100
 nikad izliječe nisi.

1418
00:52:43,600 --> 00:52:45,180
 ali kad ideš ovim putem,

1419
00:52:45,180 --> 00:52:49,240
 onda Bog ide s tobom

1420
00:52:49,240 --> 00:52:51,020
 iz djavlje od njega

1421
00:52:51,020 --> 00:52:51,440
 bježe.

1422
00:52:51,440 --> 00:52:55,100
 Ima jedan mladi čovjek,

1423
00:52:55,100 --> 00:52:58,480
 supruga mu ima velikih problema,

1424
00:52:58,480 --> 00:52:59,700
 tlačenja duhovnih,

1425
00:52:59,700 --> 00:53:02,400
 i kad god on moli za nju,

1426
00:53:02,400 --> 00:53:03,580
 njom bude lakše,

1427
00:53:03,580 --> 00:53:04,640
 njoj bude lakše.

1428
00:53:06,020 --> 00:53:06,880
 I jedan put kaže,

1429
00:53:06,880 --> 00:53:08,440
 molio sam tako za ženu,

1430
00:53:08,440 --> 00:53:10,160
 iskočio mi tlak 220.

1431
00:53:10,160 --> 00:53:12,180
 Odem doktoru,

1432
00:53:12,180 --> 00:53:13,060
 dadne mi ljekove,

1433
00:53:13,060 --> 00:53:16,280
 pa što da ja pijem te ljekove ili ne,

1434
00:53:16,280 --> 00:53:16,500
 rekao.

1435
00:53:16,500 --> 00:53:17,920
 Pa pij kada ti je doktor dao,

1436
00:53:17,920 --> 00:53:18,700
 ali moli Isusa,

1437
00:53:18,700 --> 00:53:19,540
 ako nije potrebno,

1438
00:53:19,540 --> 00:53:20,800
 nek nadahne doktora da,

1439
00:53:20,800 --> 00:53:24,140
 da te skine s tih ljekova.

1440
00:53:24,140 --> 00:53:26,300
 Evo njega drugi put na svetoj misli.

1441
00:53:26,300 --> 00:53:27,900
 E, bio sam kod doktora i rekao,

1442
00:53:27,900 --> 00:53:29,360
 znaš šta, nisam ja siguran

1443
00:53:29,360 --> 00:53:31,440
 da tebi to treba,

1444
00:53:31,440 --> 00:53:33,460
 ajmo mi probati bez ljekova.

1445
00:53:33,460 --> 00:53:35,980
 Poslije toga dolazi i kaže,

1446
00:53:36,020 --> 00:53:38,840
 bojim se da nisam sletio s pameti,

1447
00:53:38,840 --> 00:53:40,460
 da nisam psihičko obolio.

1448
00:53:40,460 --> 00:53:41,720
 Šta ti je sad?

1449
00:53:41,720 --> 00:53:43,620
 Pa ne znam, kaže,

1450
00:53:43,620 --> 00:53:46,180
 prate me nekakvi glasovi.

1451
00:53:46,180 --> 00:53:48,540
 Govori, ja sam visoki tlak,

1452
00:53:48,540 --> 00:53:50,080
 ja sam rak debelog strijeva,

1453
00:53:50,080 --> 00:53:51,160
 ja sam rak pluća,

1454
00:53:51,160 --> 00:53:52,520
 ja sam ovaj sve neke bolesti

1455
00:53:52,520 --> 00:53:53,360
 i govori ja sam.

1456
00:53:53,360 --> 00:53:54,340
 I jedan od njih kaže,

1457
00:53:54,340 --> 00:53:56,960
 ne stvara Bog bolesti,

1458
00:53:56,960 --> 00:53:57,920
 nego mi.

1459
00:53:57,920 --> 00:54:00,860
 Rekao, to ti je istina.

1460
00:54:00,860 --> 00:54:03,400
 Bog stvara i obnavlja.

1461
00:54:05,120 --> 00:54:06,340
 stvara i obnavlja.

1462
00:54:06,340 --> 00:54:08,180
 Ništa nije uništio što je stvorio.

1463
00:54:08,180 --> 00:54:11,820
 Sotona i demoni uništavaju.

1464
00:54:11,820 --> 00:54:12,540
 To je istina.

1465
00:54:12,540 --> 00:54:14,560
 I onda se sjetim,

1466
00:54:14,560 --> 00:54:16,200
 ovoga,

1467
00:54:16,200 --> 00:54:17,640
 negdje početkom vrata,

1468
00:54:17,640 --> 00:54:18,680
 čistio sam garažu,

1469
00:54:18,680 --> 00:54:19,680
 a kuća u nizu,

1470
00:54:19,680 --> 00:54:21,100
 pa propuh da mi vuče

1471
00:54:21,100 --> 00:54:23,760
 od prednjih vrata

1472
00:54:23,760 --> 00:54:24,820
 u dvorište,

1473
00:54:25,220 --> 00:54:26,540
 prašinu dok metem

1474
00:54:26,540 --> 00:54:28,900
 i dva šišmiša lete

1475
00:54:28,900 --> 00:54:31,340
 i krilom

1476
00:54:31,340 --> 00:54:32,940
 pukne me po glavi.

1477
00:54:32,940 --> 00:54:34,200
 I ode tamo,

1478
00:54:34,200 --> 00:54:34,860
 naježi se,

1479
00:54:34,860 --> 00:54:36,620
 pa reko nije mu se radar pokvario,

1480
00:54:36,620 --> 00:54:37,480
 kako me je pogodio.

1481
00:54:37,480 --> 00:54:41,140
 Vraća se iz onog dvorišta,

1482
00:54:41,140 --> 00:54:42,600
 opet me lupi po glavi.

1483
00:54:43,980 --> 00:54:45,120
 Ja se naježi rako,

1484
00:54:45,120 --> 00:54:46,440
 Bože, ovo nešto nije normalno.

1485
00:54:46,440 --> 00:54:48,220
 Eto ih opet lete,

1486
00:54:48,220 --> 00:54:49,480
 kona dva iz našibenika.

1487
00:54:49,480 --> 00:54:52,280
 Ja kažem u ime Isusa,

1488
00:54:52,280 --> 00:54:53,060
 na zarećenina,

1489
00:54:53,060 --> 00:54:54,420
 zapovjedam ti zli duše,

1490
00:54:54,420 --> 00:54:55,260
 odstupi od mene,

1491
00:54:55,260 --> 00:54:56,620
 ja nisam tvoj nego Kristov,

1492
00:54:56,620 --> 00:54:58,620
 u ime Oca i Sina i Duha Svetoga.

1493
00:54:58,620 --> 00:54:59,020
 Amen.

1494
00:54:59,020 --> 00:55:02,360
 Odoše,

1495
00:55:02,360 --> 00:55:03,340
 raširiše se

1496
00:55:03,340 --> 00:55:05,000
 i nisu se više vratili.

1497
00:55:05,000 --> 00:55:06,980
 I nije ti sve jedno,

1498
00:55:06,980 --> 00:55:08,820
 gađaju te točno.

1499
00:55:08,820 --> 00:55:13,740
 I za toga meni počne riječići.

1500
00:55:13,980 --> 00:55:16,140
 sarkom,

1501
00:55:16,140 --> 00:55:17,940
 sarkom,

1502
00:55:17,940 --> 00:55:19,780
 istim tempom konišišmiši.

1503
00:55:19,780 --> 00:55:20,760
 Sarkom,

1504
00:55:20,760 --> 00:55:22,400
 a baš mi jedna prijateljica obrva

1505
00:55:22,400 --> 00:55:24,320
 od sarkoma pluća,

1506
00:55:24,320 --> 00:55:26,300
 neizlječivi rak,

1507
00:55:26,300 --> 00:55:27,120
 je li?

1508
00:55:27,120 --> 00:55:28,760
 Najježiš se.

1509
00:55:28,760 --> 00:55:29,100
 Ja kažem,

1510
00:55:29,100 --> 00:55:29,820
 zli duše,

1511
00:55:29,820 --> 00:55:31,920
 sarkom zapovjedam ti u ime Isusovo,

1512
00:55:31,920 --> 00:55:32,680
 odstupi od mene,

1513
00:55:32,680 --> 00:55:34,160
 ja nisam tvoj nego Kristov.

1514
00:55:34,160 --> 00:55:37,920
 I prestane taj glas unutra koji,

1515
00:55:37,920 --> 00:55:38,940
 nisi ga mogo istirati.

1516
00:55:38,940 --> 00:55:41,660
 I to sam shvatio,

1517
00:55:41,660 --> 00:55:42,440
 čekaj, čekaj.

1518
00:55:43,740 --> 00:55:45,460
 Sotona koji je destruktivac,

1519
00:55:45,460 --> 00:55:47,160
 koji ruši ono što je stvoreno,

1520
00:55:47,160 --> 00:55:50,320
 on se kao otac laži prikriva

1521
00:55:50,320 --> 00:55:52,620
 pod medicinska imena.

1522
00:55:52,620 --> 00:55:53,820
 Pa onda tu ne očekuješ

1523
00:55:53,820 --> 00:55:54,940
 da bi djavo mogao biti,

1524
00:55:54,940 --> 00:55:56,520
 e onda od tada stanu, molim,

1525
00:55:56,520 --> 00:55:57,640
 zli duše,

1526
00:55:57,640 --> 00:55:59,180
 pa pročitam diagnozu.

1527
00:55:59,180 --> 00:56:00,960
 Ja nisam tvoj nego Kristov,

1528
00:56:00,960 --> 00:56:01,960
 gospodine,

1529
00:56:01,960 --> 00:56:03,080
 ti se bori protiv njega,

1530
00:56:03,080 --> 00:56:04,720
 ja nisam njegov nego tvoji.

1531
00:56:06,100 --> 00:56:08,360
 Moji se liječe i ne izliječe,

1532
00:56:08,360 --> 00:56:10,140
 a meni odlaze tako bolesti.

1533
00:56:10,140 --> 00:56:14,360
 I onda se dogodi da me zove žena iz Mostara,

1534
00:56:14,360 --> 00:56:16,520
 iz Mostarske bolnice,

1535
00:56:16,520 --> 00:56:16,900
 kaže,

1536
00:56:16,900 --> 00:56:17,520
 gospodine,

1537
00:56:17,520 --> 00:56:18,700
 moli vas,

1538
00:56:18,700 --> 00:56:19,520
 pomolite se,

1539
00:56:19,520 --> 00:56:20,440
 kad god ste molili,

1540
00:56:20,440 --> 00:56:21,260
 bilo mi je lakše,

